@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Usuario" as U
participant "App Móvil" as APP
database "Secure Storage\n(Almacenamiento local)" as SS
participant "Servidor" as SRV
database "DB Usuarios" as DB

== Registro de Usuario ==

U -> APP: Introduce Teléfono y Master Key
APP -> APP: Generar Password remota aleatoria
APP -> APP: Generar EC KeyPair (Curva P-256, Pub/Priv)
APP -> SS: Guardar Clave Privada, Master Key\n(SecureRandom)\n y Password remota aleatoria

APP -> APP: SHA-256(Password)
APP -> SRV: Enviar Teléfono, Clave Pública,\nSHA-256(Password)

SRV -> SRV: HMAC-SHA-256(Teléfono, Pepper_1)\nPara indexado O(1)
SRV -> SRV: Argon2id(Hash_Pass, Salt, Pepper_2)

SRV -> DB: Guardar Teléfono HMAC-SHA-256, Clave Pública\ny Hash de Password Argon2id
SRV --> APP: Registro Exitoso
@enduml
